data.description: Come see this 3-bedroom / 2.5-bathroom, end unit in Flowery Branches Tide Water Cove. This home offers a newly renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, and tile flooring. It offers spacious bedrooms, primary bathroom with double vanity. Conveniently located to downtown, lakeside dining, marinas, shopping and I-985. Don't miss out on this one!
